definitions.definition: Either of two species of large amphibious reptile , Alligator mississippiensis or Alligator sinensis , in the genus Alligator within order Crocodilia , which have sharp teeth and very strong jaws and are native to the Americas and China, respectively.
A member of the family Alligatoridae , which includes the caimans .
Any of various machines with strong jaws , one of which opens like the movable jaw of an alligator.

subdefinitions.definition: A form of squeezer for the puddle ball .

definitions.definition: Any of various vehicles that have relatively long, low noses in front of a cab or other, usually windowed, structure.
A swing music fan or performer, especially one who is white .

main_definition: Either of two species of large amphibious reptile , Alligator mississippiensis or Alligator sinensis , in the genus Alligator within order Crocodilia , which have sharp teeth and very strong jaws and are native to the Americas and China, respectively.
secondary_definitions: ( paleontology ) A member of the family Alligatoridae , which includes the caimans .
( Nigeria ) A dwarf crocodile ( Osteolaemus tetraspis )
( dated ) A crocodile of any species.
Any of various machines with strong jaws , one of which opens like the movable jaw of an alligator.
Any of various vehicles that have relatively long, low noses in front of a cab or other, usually windowed, structure.
( usually in the plural ) An alligator-skin shoe.
( US , slang , dated ) A swing music fan or performer, especially one who is white .
